00:12:03.339 --> 00:12:08.019
wonderful is my Savior's love to me. The reason that we know that is because He

00:12:08.019 --> 00:12:13.659
declared His love to us, and He spoke, and we think about the spoken Word of God, the

00:12:13.659 --> 00:12:18.779
power of His Word. We're thankful to have the written Word of God that we're able

00:12:18.779 --> 00:12:23.219
to go to and read it and study it and memorize it, meditate upon it, and we're

