the creation account, once again we're reminded of the declaration. I want you

00:12:40.639 --> 00:12:44.119
to notice, however, as we think of these land-based animals, I want you to

00:12:44.119 --> 00:12:48.639
notice the distinction that God makes in verses 24 and 25. He makes this

00:12:48.639 --> 00:12:53.319
distinction, and really, in verses 24 and 25, He is speaking in broad terms or

00:12:53.319 --> 00:12:58.519
categories that He would use in distinguishing the types of animals that

